 denial reasons helps you develop an action plan:"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "How do ITIN mortgage payments impact your tax situation?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Can ITIN borrowers deduct mortgage interest on tax returns? Yes\u2014ITIN holders have the same tax benefits as citizens:"}}]};
